things should be available

00:18:11.290 --> 00:18:12.980
to everyone, you know.

00:18:12.980 --> 00:18:21.680
And I feel that a lot of
places around the world

00:18:21.680 --> 00:18:31.150
that have done this
really well have done this

00:18:31.150 --> 00:18:34.500
with a great amount of success.

00:18:34.500 --> 00:18:44.730 position:56%
