of taking jazz music and taking it

00:18:44.730 --> 00:18:52.000 position:56%
to places where it's not you know --
where people are not as accustomed

00:18:52.000 --> 00:18:54.970
to seeing it or having it around

00:18:54.970 --> 00:18:59.660
and just giving them the
opportunity to be exposed.

00:18:59.660 --> 00:19:07.730
You know, I don't really see it as
a way of commercializing the music

00:19:07.730 --> 00:19:13.270
or opening up the gap to
one audience or anything.

00:19:13.270 --> 00:19:20.100
I just feel like it's important
for people to be exposed to as much

00:19:20.100 --> 00:19:24.580
as possible and let them decide
if this stuff is for them or not.

00:19:24.580 --> 00:19:29.090 position:56%
So this idea became the reality in
part with the help of this injection

00:19:29.090 --> 00:19:31.750
