being able to get there, play,

00:21:25.780 --> 00:21:27.960
connecting with someone
and have them just enjoy it

00:21:27.960 --> 00:21:29.370
for the sake of music.

00:21:29.370 --> 00:21:31.610
For me it's been super rewarding.

